snippet.textDisplay:
* THIS IS TOTALLY FAKE *
I know some production people who have FIRST HAND knowledge of this ridiculous farse. Do you REALLY believe prisoners eat like that in prisons? Beef Wellington? Really? Cmon' people. If you believe even ONE second of this then you are truly, truly stupid. Almost ALL "reality shows" are fake. Pawn Stars, American Pickers, Naked and Afraid...the list is endless.

When you're in prison you get a slice of bread, a slab of rubbery chicken or a low quality beef patty and some boiled vegetables. There are no carving knives. They have a can opening machine that they put the can in and it LOCKS. The can is opened and the sharp lid falls into a vault. EVERY can and lid is counted so the CO's can account for them and make sure no weapons are made. And no..I have never been in prison.
